==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Zinco-polar
<hw>Zin`co-po"lar</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Zinco-</ets> + <ets>polar</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Elec.)</fld>
<def>Electrically polarized like the surface of the zinc presented to
the acid in a battery, which has zincous affinity.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Zincous</ent>⟦br⟧
